evaluation.overall_comment:
This is a high-quality translation that successfully conveys the educational, conversational tone of the original French podcast while accurately delivering complex AI concepts to a Spanish-speaking audience. The structure is logical, the flow is generally natural, and all technical information is preserved without omission. Minor deductions are due to a few domain-specific terminology slips ('afinamiento' instead of 'ajuste fino', 'ancrage' left in French) and a couple of typographical/idiomatic inconsistencies ('Porque' vs 'Por qué', formal phrasing). With minor technical polishing, this would be publication-ready for a specialized tech audience. Overall, it fulfills its communicative purpose excellently and aligns with high-quality translation standards.
{score}18
{/score}
